        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`apollo-server-express`}</code>{` under the hood).`}</p>
    <blockquote>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`We recommend Express because it's the most popular Node.js web framework, and it integrates well with many `}<em parentName="p">{`other`}</em>{` popular libraries. It does have its limitations (for example, Express async support is not built around `}<code parentName="p" {...{
